{"tid":2102547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美政府：你要使用華為等公司的產品， 就別想賺我的錢","createTime":"2020-07-10T14:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T14:59:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a00b65128bc1bad6b01dd320b115b7357365f8","tid":2102547,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"美政府：你要使用華為等公司的產品， 就別想賺我的錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/companies-using-huawei-banned-from-us-government-07092020/5496587.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fcompanies-using-huawei-banned-from-us-government-07092020%2F5496587.html&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumlu%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=533cbd94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/companies-using-huawei-banned-from-us-government-07092020/5496587.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有報導說，美國政府將很快出台規定，禁止使用五家中國公司產品的公司獲得美國政府的承包合同。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">路透社9日報導說，特朗普政府計劃本週推出規定，禁止聯邦政府將採購合同授予使用中國華為、海康威視、大華技術股份、海能達通信和中興公司產品的任何企業。任何在日常運營中使用這五家中國公司產品的企業，如果依然希望獲得美國政府的採購合同，就需要獲得美國政府的豁免。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n路透社說，這項規定可能會對與美國政府保持商業往來的公司產生深遠的影響，因為他們現在需要證明沒有使用浙江大華技術或海康威視的產品，而這兩家中國企業生產的監視設備和攝像機在全球市場中屬暢銷產品。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">路透社舉例說，亞馬遜公司今年4月就從浙江大華技術公司購買了1500台攝像機，用來在疫情期間測試員工的體溫。而亞馬遜公司的雲端服務是美國情報機構的主要承包商，目前正在與微軟公司爭奪​​價值可達100億美元的美國國防部的雲計算合約。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">路透社說，這項規定將由聯邦採辦管理委員會（Federal Acquisition Regulatory Council）發布，計劃8月13日生效。白宮方面明確表示，規定的執行不會拖延，而且要獲得豁免是很難的。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n白宮管理和預算辦公室（Office of Management and Budget）代理主任瓦特（Russ Vought）對路透社說，&ldquo;中國等試圖對我們的體制進行滲透的海外敵對國家讓我們國家面臨巨大的危險&rdquo;，&ldquo;特朗普政府充分實施聯邦採辦禁令，可以讓我們的政府持續強大，免受華為等邪惡網絡的侵害&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n國會政府問責局（Government Accountability Office）的數字顯示，美國政府每年簽訂的採購合約價值超過5000億美元。"},{"pid":"af35c6599e47f807e108cdb1f7ffef45dd914088","tid":2102547,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354d1015281312d9db9152b108b6df534db877ff","tid":2102547,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"great news"},{"pid":"a0f310dde8670afc99dfdd6fb8d61ac9c3aa8813","tid":2102547,"uid":8880,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"想吃美國飯不能砸美國鍋<br />\n用返五毛d金句笑返五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381c93ba5732941c4736dce580a05841bbe76610","tid":2102547,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9910a287e5ceab8353d53fe3d372c473b87200e5","tid":2102547,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"因小細大"},{"pid":"c366934e96856d5a3aafdf2016722f61586655be","tid":2102547,"uid":281180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"美國黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"b4e6f815e5d953ea2d132cc35cea93981cf61858","tid":2102547,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e3d5ab04519c827b1768cd8d9355c817e28098","tid":2102547,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"美國正！"}]}